Dear Raffaella,

I hope you had a great weekend.
Regarding your privacy request submitted on 10 October, we kindly request a=
n extension until 7 November 2025, due to the significant scope of work inv=
olved.

Please feel free to reach out if you have any questions.

We appreciate your understanding and look forward to your response.

Kind regards,
[cid:image001.png@01DC41B9.15E756B0]
Privacy Team
Level 5, 136 Fanshawe Street,
PO Box 90347, Auckland 1142
